<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 7: VIBRATION DAMPER, CRANKSHAFT, MAIN
        BEARINGS, FLYWHEEL AND CRANKCASE - INSTALLING THE FLYWHEEL
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>INSTALLING THE FLYWHEEL</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>Install the flywheel as follows: (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600730">7.30</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
            <title>INSTALLING</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install two (2) flywheel guide studs
                    <emph type="bold">ZTSE4375</emph>
                    into the 3 and 9 o'clock positions of the crankshaft.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install flywheel over guide studs and secure to crankshaft with ten (10) flywheel
                    mounting bolts.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>
                            <emph type="underscr">FOR APPLICATIONS USING AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSIONS</emph>, INSTALL SPACER,
                            FLEXPLATE(S) AND REINFORCING RING, THEN INSTALL THE TEN (10) FLYWHEEL MOUNTING BOLTS.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove two (2) guide studs and install remaining two (2) mounting bolts. Tighten all
                    twelve (12) flywheel mounting bolts to the special torque value (
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1600731">7.31</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <figure id="ef1600730" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5098" filename="../figeg5/EG5098.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 7.30 Installing Flywheel Guide Studs</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
                        <callout1 type="arabic">1. Flywheel Guide Studs</callout1>
                    </calloutgroup>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1600731" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg5097" filename="../figeg5/EG5097.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 7.31 Installing Flywheel</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
